ebaj2005_figurines.shp -- a feature class showing the locations of recovered figurines.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"wzxOB6q5ft"}],"key":"dY3e5Xmfnw"}],"key":"BSyA2GeTfY"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"In addition, you will need to acquire SRTM data for this lab and refer to the mounds you digitized in Lab 2.","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"uYd2laDXxJ"}],"key":"WKlqCHFKr7"}],"key":"NASKAhYDUu"}],"key":"nQjkvYTUZM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"For this lab:","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"bHwiXZyrYy"}],"key":"tNVZtv33as"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Download SRTM (Shuttle Radar Topography Mission) digital elevation model (DEM) data over the archaeological site of San Andres Semetebaj. Download both the SRTM 1 Arc-Second Global and the SRTM Void Filled rasters. What are the differences between these two rasters? Are there any issues with these data in the study region? Note that to view differences appropriately, you must have a single layer checked in the Contents at a time.","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"UEuygE5CVB"}],"key":"ezKucb5jKH"}],"key":"U5Kq7R3Q0S"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":